<h2 class="nsw-h3">Offset grids</h2>
<p>Use <code>nsw-offset-lg-*</code> to shift the column to the right to the number of columns specified. For example, a <code>nsw-offset-lg-3</code> class will have a 3-column gap between the previous column.</p>
{{#>_docs-example separated="true"}}
